Xinhua Xinhua Agency, Beijing, Dec.11 (Xinhua)-On December 11, President Xi Jinping sent a congratulatory letter to the 2021 Dawan District Science Forum. Xi Jinping pointed out that the world today is undergoing great changes not seen in a century, and global scientific and technological innovation has entered an intensive and active period.The new round of scientific and technological revolution and industrial transformation has had a profound impact on the global economic structure. The Guangdong-Hong Kong-Macao Greater Bay Area should focus on the strategic positioning of building an international science and technology innovation center, strive to build a global science and technology innovation highland, and promote the development of emerging industries. China is willing to work with scientists and international science and technology organizations around the world to strengthen international scientific and technological exchanges and cooperation, strengthen research on major scientific issues, promote common science and technology solutions, and deepen cooperation on key scientific projects.Jointly promote the development of world science and better benefit mankind. The 2021 Dawan District Science Forum was opened in Guangzhou City, Guangdong Province on the same day, with the theme of "Exploring the Future, Sharing Science", hosted by the People's Government of Guangdong Province.
